Evicted a squatted farm where macrofiestas were made
The invaders had taken possession of 11 of the 13 floors of the building, in Balmes, 51.
The 12 occupants left the farm yesterday noon without resistance
Everything seems to indicate that the nightmare lived by the neighbors of 51 Balmes Street has come to an end.
Twelve people voluntarily left yesterday’s noon the building they illegally occupied, and where they organized macrofiestas that despaired the neighborhood, by court order and without the need for police intervention.
